{"tid":799904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【季經】細個有咩威水史","createTime":"2018-08-30T12:24:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T12:47:34.000Z","uid":131822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62083bf0269ba16f167dc058562e12de64105c4b","tid":799904,"uid":131822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"記得以前中學參加CoCo 比賽<br />\n叫乜乜掃描霸戰王咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次同朋友去<br />\n入到決賽輸咗<br />\n唔緊要<br />\n我同自己講<br />\n「話哂全港第二! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n然後CoCo下期見到 有自己名同相<br />\n即刻覺得好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後主辦單位再舉辦多一次<br />\n多次又入到決賽<br />\n結果拎咗全港冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最開心係當時冠軍獎品係PSP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮撚的童年就係狂打PSP <br />\n<br />\n然後人大了<br />\n發現自己好平庸<br />\n係一個咁鳩嘅比賽<br />\n拎全港第一<br />\n真係要慶祝下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ae13a567089e5293516d0f0090eef6397b5f39","tid":799904,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"有錢"},{"pid":"91646a286bb6d3f639eaee42b1887e7e50229944","tid":799904,"uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"六歲開始打飛機"},{"pid":"fe9d551873761d42bc05ce54541615640baf8381","tid":799904,"uid":199026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"喺小學4樓唔小心dum左個書包落操場"},{"pid":"fd523eabefd40e7a56da95ac13273edb00df8c7d","tid":799904,"uid":194687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23f59a4d48656dee7cebf0419643655d326b89c4","tid":799904,"uid":155509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"三歲識用針線縫野，從未拮過自己手"},{"pid":"6f79443f6445cd7d0a556f56c8e22f70